WEBVTT

00:02:58.632 --> 00:03:01.909
Venom can also paralyze you
almost instantly,

00:03:01.933 --> 00:03:05.752
or it can just eat
your flesh away, like acid.

00:03:06.456 --> 00:03:10.789
Now, all of these are pretty
gruesome stories, I know,

00:03:10.813 --> 00:03:14.155
but, to me, it's kind of music to my ears.

00:03:14.179 --> 00:03:15.591
It's what I love.

00:03:15.615 --> 00:03:16.765
So why is that?

00:03:17.314 --> 00:03:19.776
Well, it's not because I'm a nutcase, no.

00:03:19.800 --> 00:03:21.474
(Laughter)

00:03:21.498 --> 00:03:24.712
Just imagine what we could do

00:03:24.736 --> 00:03:28.753
if we could harvest
all those super powerful compounds

00:03:28.777 --> 00:03:31.049
and use them to our benefit.